# Nextcloud All-in-One
# Public domain: nextcloud.psimaker.org
#
# AIO bootstraps every dependent container (Apache, database, Redis, Talk,
# imaginary, fulltextsearch) from inside the master container by talking to
# the host Docker socket. Operational config — admin password, S3 backend,
# domain — lives in the AIO web UI on :8080, not here.
#
# This compose file therefore needs no env vars. The file is kept so the
# directory shape matches every other stack.
